<h1>2盒踏尽网<!--img src="style/netkeiba.ja/image/race_grade_g2_01.png" alt=""--></h1>
<p>
<diary_snap_cut>
<span>
ダ宝1400m&nbsp;/&nbsp;
欧铬 : 啦&nbsp;/&nbsp;
